   The glare of the weapons on the wall seem to 
   temporarily blind you as you enter. Many of
   them are very much, covered with blood. In 
   the middle of the room you see a huge shrine
   which seems to emit lava. It seems to give off
   a thumping sound like that of a heartbeat. As 
   you look around you see the only exit to the 
   west. Upon the gate there lies a huge lock that
   has the name Master written on it. I think you
   need a key for that.  Now where could it be?

