#22373
Before the Bridge of Faith~

   As you exit the gates, you come before a very
   unstable looking bridge. It is made entirely
   wood and has NO rails. It sways from side to
   side. The bridge is stretched across a pit,
   towards a cave on the other side. As you 
   look into the pit, you see many skeletons
   of warriors who have failed the test of faith
   and have fallen to their deaths and were
   impaled by the spikes. Have faith and believe
   that it was you who was destined to overthrow
   this beast known as Shao Kahn.

